{"tid":1380901,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"Bio Sciences：獨立調查委員會 整死香港冇命賠","createTime":"2019-07-29T06:25:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T07:54:54.000Z","uid":190521,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8cd35e3b362e70f44596d04772242c4563f8c4ad","tid":1380901,"uid":190521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:25:39.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">獨立調查委員會 整死香港冇命賠</span></strong></div><br />\n香港所面對的問題是制度崩壞，是主權問題。而獨立調查委員會，必定受制於在現行的制度。在崩壞的制度中，根本沒有可能進行合理的調查。<br />\n<br />\n又或者誠實問一下自己，你期望獨立調查委員會能做到甚麼？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">就看看以往這類獨立調查委員會能做到的事情</span>。港鐵沙中線的紅磡站工程，嚴重違規，甚至有倒垮危險。調查後有公司要賠償嗎？有高層要負上刑事責任嗎？面對一所公司，這類委員會尚且不能作出任何實際行動，你認為委員會面對中共殖民香港政府可以有甚麼實際作用？<br />\n<br />\n會起訴三萬名警？立即 22 條立法？裁定中聯辦違法？罷免林鄭、盧偉聰？<br />\n<br />\n這些都不會發生。<br />\n<br />\n那麼獨立調查委員會有何作用？作用就大了。是等同談判。<strong>一方面，香港人會分化成調查派和不調查派，示威力量就減弱</strong>。另一方面，<strong>政府就能買時間，不斷拘捕所有人，製造白色恐怖。更重要，<span style=\"color: red;\">獨立調查委員是肯定了政府的管治合法性</span>，而我們是要否定香港非法政府的管治權，徹底背道而馳！</strong><br />\n<br />\n要香港恢復和平是可以的，但絕不是成立獨立調查委員會。而是逼令中共放手，是國會普選，甚或乎放棄香港主權。<br />\n<br />\n香港人現在投降，就愧對所有流過的血！愧對死去的烈士！香港要奮勇作戰下去！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/67488580_712121652570606_3676584622050770944_n.jpg?_nc_cat=111&amp;_nc_oc=AQkDMgRjxnKDnYelEwqJKCH3aVJcEE8erK3gXXjmpXnDApvs2gstlcoT08KCG67Hxlk&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-1.xx&amp;oh=6bcfef6590fce5b36e9726e908ce3809&amp;oe=5DEE8BBB\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F67488580_712121652570606_3676584622050770944_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D111%26_nc_oc%3DAQkDMgRjxnKDnYelEwqJKCH3aVJcEE8erK3gXXjmpXnDApvs2gstlcoT08KCG67Hxlk%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-1.xx%26oh%3D6bcfef6590fce5b36e9726e908ce3809%26oe%3D5DEE8BBB&h=906a6f99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/67287099_712121659237272_5840775310580121600_n.jpg?_nc_cat=108&amp;_nc_oc=AQlhuQALpUxiV3GmjQBX84IjnkhWGckjLksjMr7k65m5DvRrM1GDmWCzUTUWEbKDfsA&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-1.xx&amp;oh=15fab66afbb7fc89eb914b756d49487b&amp;oe=5DDAE88B\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F67287099_712121659237272_5840775310580121600_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D108%26_nc_oc%3DAQlhuQALpUxiV3GmjQBX84IjnkhWGckjLksjMr7k65m5DvRrM1GDmWCzUTUWEbKDfsA%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-1.xx%26oh%3D15fab66afbb7fc89eb914b756d49487b%26oe%3D5DDAE88B&h=5d90e0c2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8bf263df7a0d309e7e3dab089e2efc38bd143fe2","tid":1380901,"uid":190521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:26:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=712121762570595&amp;id=347501365699305\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D712121762570595%26id%3D347501365699305&d=WXcHt8yLUpgx7cmMWxn67ZKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=e2523713\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=712121762570595&amp;id=347501365699305</a>"},{"pid":"83d647bdd7113d631e3843e2714094a273dcc41b","tid":1380901,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:54:13.000Z","msg":"其實調查係需要既，不過係由邊個調查咁解，就算七婆順攤話搞，佢都可能係搵D土共做戲咋"},{"pid":"4a63803c3afba2d0d0fe2a7dee5f1cad88cd2098","tid":1380901,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:54:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">而家係連戲都唔肯做比你 驚有變數 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日(7月29)1500-1830</span></span>會有義工係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">旺角東天橋</span></span>擺街站等無上連登的市民都可以寫底感受比我地,希望大家支持<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【眾籌】 已集合超過1000名巴絲感想 香港編年史</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blan